name: BabyBuzz
0:
”Alexa start Baby Buzz”
”Alexa open Baby Buzz”
”it's a cat”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: baby buzz
des: A fun game to teach different words like names of fruits, vegetables, animals, colors, days, months, planets etc to toddlers during the early development stage. Helps with memory and kills boredom. Just start the skill, listen to the category and reply with a name. You can skip by saying 'Next' or repeat the old one by saying 'Previous' or repeat the existing one by saying 'Repeat'. To terminate and exit the game, say 'Stop'.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
